      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773937373499,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Supervised Data - Labelled data as harmful contents, NSFW datasets\n\nSemi-Supervised Data - User reports for using proxy label is likely correlated with the true label\n\nSelf-Supervised Data - User comments for using good signals for harmful contents\n\nContent features - texts from post body, hashtags, etc.  images attached to a post\n\nBehavior features - # comments, # negative reactions ( hides, blocks, etc), ratio of shares to views\n\nUser embeddings - trained user profiles, account age, user context features (real-time aggregates of import signals)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Supervised Data - Labelled data as harmful contents, NSFW datasets\n\nSemi-Supervised Data - User reports for using proxy label is likely correlated with the true label\n\nSelf-Supervised Data - User comments for using good signals for harmful contents\n\nContent features - texts from post body, hashtags, etc.  images attached to a post\n\nBehavior features - # comments, # negative reactions ( hides, blocks, etc), ratio of shares to views\n\nUser embeddings - trained user profiles, account age, user context features (real-time aggregates of import signals)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
