      "index": "b3D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1342752891,
      "version": 255,
      "versionNonce": 1792157872,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773971792979,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Evaluation\n\nOnline\nImportance sampling\nHeavily sample accounts near decision boundaries where models disagree\nDown-sample obvious cases (scores near 0.0 or 1.0) with appropriate reweighting\nFocus labeling budget on accounts with high potential user impact\n\nOffline\n\nPrecision @Recall90\nPR-AUC\nImpact-Weighted Metrics\n\nEarly detection rate\nNetwork coverage\n\nFairness evaluation\nAdversarial robustness - red team dataset\nDetect drift\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Evaluation\n\nOnline\nImportance sampling\nHeavily sample accounts near decision boundaries where models disagree\nDown-sample obvious cases (scores near 0.0 or 1.0) with appropriate reweighting\nFocus labeling budget on accounts with high potential user impact\n\nOffline\n\nPrecision @Recall90\nPR-AUC\nImpact-Weighted Metrics\n\nEarly detection rate\nNetwork coverage\n\nFairness evaluation\nAdversarial robustness - red team dataset\nDetect drift\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
